settings.description: Well, the objective is stupidly simple. Find the right level and don't do all that hard work for nothing! P-Wing included for special time wasting! Careful as something may block your path.

Welcome to the Museum! Come gawk at some of the strange critters that are native to the Mushroom Kingdom!
Difficulty: 1/5

Hit the switches! But where's that dang 3rd Ace Coin!?
Difficulty: 3.5/5

I was trying to make something similar to an actual E-Reader level. Bullet Battlefield was what I came up with.
A unique idea of a triangular level.
A quick level that focuses on rotating platforms. Keep your eye out for any Advance Coins you come in contact with along the way!
Ya know, while fire snakes are meant to be reddish orange... they look really good with a cool blue, so... why not build a nice chilly sky level featuring them for one?~
No low budget flagpole this time!
I was looking through the site after playing the classic e-reader levels and thought "hmm... I wonder if I should upload the rest of SMB..."
Rattle me bones! the big boo's new fortress is filled with bones and boos! think you can find the special treasure and take down the boss?
Suppose it's time for an old washed up mario flash level maker to step foot into a new light... with a new honestly great level making program as well! hopefully this level's fun too!
